{
  "stem": "14060.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I, I, I am very hard put to believe that either in Hungary or in Slovakia or Austria-- where I go very often and I know the people; I speak the language-- people have changed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Yes, there was a period from '45 to early '60s, mid-'60s, when they kept quiet, and it was always the other one who did it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they don't know about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they are surprised, and they are so sorry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when they met you, they couldn't say enough terrible sort of excuses how such terrible thing could have happened, and they just didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, I have yet to believe that the whole of continent of Europe didn't know what was going on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Anyway, so that is as far as the Slovakian jury is concerned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then I would like to proceed as to what was happening in our town and to my knowledge-- actual, personal knowledge of it.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "In the late '30s-- and particularly there was an emphasis put on by the Hungarian government, the [NON-ENGLISH] governed with various types of prime ministers.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Some were more anti-Semitic than others.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were better ones.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH] he was better than [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You know, this, of course, has changed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "That all Hungarian Jews had to prove their Hungarian nationality.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that was not a mean task, because not everybody-- those days, people didn't travel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They didn't have passports.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We did, as it happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We used to go every year-- summer holidays to summering in Austria.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And that is, just as I touched it, we used to go there every year.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "The last time we were there was in 1937.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And it was a place called Villa [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "It is-- the [NON-ENGLISH], which is the main hotel, very close by next to the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
